<br />
when your crowd control is just a root (whether done by a wizard or any other root-enabled class) everyone needs to pay attention to where they are standing and where all the mobs are in the camp.  sometimes this requires a little more thought than the ideal situation where a chanter mezzes and the problem is taken care of completely.  all too often, people are not willing (or maybe not able) to expend this little bit of extra effort. <br /></div>
